---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="claure.org — Homelab Automation, AI Tools & Self-Hosting Resources"
  description="Practical guides and digital tools for running a self-hosted homelab with AI automation. Built by someone who's done it."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section style="padding: 5rem 0 3rem;">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="max-width: 700px;">
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap;">
          <span class="badge badge-green">Self-hosted</span>
          <span class="badge badge-blue">AI-automated</span>
          <span class="badge badge-amber">$0 marginal cost</span>
        </div>
        <h1 style="font-size: 3rem; margin: 0 0 1.25rem; line-height: 1.2;">
          Your homelab,<br />fully automated.
        </h1>
        <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--text2); margin: 0 0 2rem; max-width: 540px;">
          Practical tools and guides for running a self-hosted infrastructure
          with AI doing 95% of the work. Real configs from a real homelab.
        </p>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap;">
          <a href="/products" class="btn btn-primary">Browse Products</a>
          <a href="/blog" class="btn btn-outline">Read the Blog</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Terminal demo -->
  <section style="padding: 2rem 0 4rem;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="terminal" style="max-width: 700px;">
        <div class="terminal-bar">
          <div class="terminal-dot red"></div>
          <div class="terminal-dot yellow"></div>
          <div class="terminal-dot green"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="terminal-body">
          <div><span class="prompt">adam@brain</span>:~/frontbot$ <span>./status.py</span></div>
          <div class="output" style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
            ✓ 17 containers running across 3 VMs<br />
            ✓ Morning brief delivered at 07:30 ET<br />
            ✓ 23 emails triaged, 7 archived automatically<br />
            ✓ Disk at 34% on all hosts (trend: stable)<br />
            <span class="highlight">↑ Revenue: $247 this week (3 new sales)</span>
          </div>
          <div style="margin-top: 0.75rem;"><span class="prompt">adam@brain</span>:~/frontbot$ <span style="opacity: 0.5;">_</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What you'll find here -->
  <section style="padding: 3rem 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--border);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>What's here</h2>
        <p>Real infrastructure, real configs. Not tutorials for beginners — tools for people who want it done.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-3">
        <div class="card">
          <div style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">📦</div>
          <h3 style="margin: 0 0 0.5rem;">Digital Products</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--text2); margin: 0; font-size: 0.9rem;">
            Packaged Ansible playbooks, Docker Compose stacks, and architecture blueprints.
            Deploy in minutes, not days.
          </p>
          <a href="/products" style="display: inline-block; margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.85rem;">Browse products →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">📝</div>
          <h3 style="margin: 0 0 0.5rem;">Technical Blog</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--text2); margin: 0; font-size: 0.9rem;">
            Deep dives on homelab architecture, AI automation patterns, and lessons learned
            running 26+ services.
          </p>
          <a href="/blog" style="display: inline-block; margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.85rem;">Read the blog →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">🤖</div>
          <h3 style="margin: 0 0 0.5rem;">AI Sysadmin</h3>
          <p style="color: var(--text2); margin: 0; font-size: 0.9rem;">
            FrontBot — a modular Python bot that manages a full homelab autonomously.
            Architecture, code, and a how-to guide.
          </p>
          <a href="/products#ai-sysadmin" style="display: inline-block; margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.85rem;">Get the blueprint →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Featured products -->
  <section style="padding: 3rem 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--border);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Popular products</h2>
        <p>Everything is a downloadable bundle. No subscriptions, no upsells.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-2">
        <div class="card" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
          <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
            <h3 style="margin: 0;">Homelab Starter Pack</h3>
            <div><span class="price">$19</span></div>
          </div>
          <p style="color: var(--text2); flex: 1; font-size: 0.9rem;">
            Complete Ansible playbooks, Docker Compose files, and service docs for a production-ready
            homelab stack. Proxmox + Docker + NPM + AdGuard + Uptime Kuma.
          </p>
          <div style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin: 1rem 0;">
            <span class="badge badge-blue">19 playbooks</span>
            <span class="badge badge-green">instant download</span>
          </div>
          <a href="/products#homelab-starter" class="btn btn-primary" style="text-align: center;">Get it →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
          <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
            <h3 style="margin: 0;">AI Sysadmin Blueprint</h3>
            <div><span class="price">$29</span></div>
          </div>
          <p style="color: var(--text2); flex: 1; font-size: 0.9rem;">
            Full FrontBot architecture: modular Python bot, 10 provider templates, Claude integration
            patterns, scheduler, and the Morning Brief pipeline.
          </p>
          <div style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin: 1rem 0;">
            <span class="badge badge-amber">Claude-powered</span>
            <span class="badge badge-green">instant download</span>
          </div>
          <a href="/products#ai-sysadmin" class="btn btn-primary" style="text-align: center;">Get it →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem;">
        <a href="/products" class="btn btn-outline">See all products →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Newsletter section -->
  <section id="newsletter" style="padding: 4rem 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--border);">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;">
        <h2 style="margin: 0 0 0.75rem;">New posts, new tools.</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--text2); margin: 0 0 1.5rem;">
          Infrequent. No fluff. When something gets built or a lesson gets learned, you'll hear about it.
        </p>
        <form
          action="https://buttondown.com/api/emails/embed-subscribe/claure"
          method="post"
          class="newsletter-form"
          style="justify-content: center;"
        >
          <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="your@email.com" required />
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Subscribe</button>
        </form>
        <p style="color: var(--text2); font-size: 0.8rem; margin: 0.75rem 0 0;">No spam. Unsubscribe anytime.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
